Package org.gwtunite.testing.generators

Class Summary
TestCaseInfoGenerator Creates the TestCaseInfo classes for all TestCases found TestCase info objects are placed in the same package as the original TestCase and be called _TestInfo
TestCaseRegistryGenerator Creates the TestCaseRegistry
TestCaseWrapperGenerator Creates a wrapper around the original test case that facilitates calling specific methods
